sg":"向渡月亭𠴱邊係有路入可以去到京都星野𠴱頭再入 d 。"},{"pid":"9528a3e2499d61877d96b5a40a994df66e764f9a","tid":108512,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:24:12.000Z","msg":"如果去天龍寺就可以再行入 d 去埋常寂光寺𠴱頭，沿路都幾好行既。"},{"pid":"24d090805e9952db111ea18c2f6f7a3cafe03152","tid":108512,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:26:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚野行上嵐山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我仲以為行得既添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200e6cc64b0b197367fea2f3b708cf020c6a9722","tid":108512,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:27:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黎緊二月中會去嵐山，睇過冇小火車<br />\n想問下有冇可能朝早行到傍晚?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nplan左會行竹林,龜山公園,天龍寺,渡月橋,嵐山公園中之島<br />\n我同男友諗住行上嵐山，但係google完全搵唔到相關資料，係咪冇得行架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n半日行完，順手浸埋溫泉就一日</blockquote><br />\n溫泉會係有馬浸，所以都未必再浸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41b386d952004b38a850042d02cbc9712749d02","tid":108512,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果去天龍寺就可以再行入 d 去埋常寂光寺𠴱頭，沿路都幾好行既。</blockquote><br />\n嗰個都應該會行埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83c032f1bd955b39d24206c91a57583cefa2497","tid":108512,"uid":1893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:28:38.000Z","msg":"大埔鳳園嵐山？"},{"pid":"262c2c22b3393a4f04621aba48b5855b0b93bfb7","tid":108512,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果去天龍寺就可以再行入 d 去埋常寂光寺𠴱頭，沿路都幾好行既。</blockquote><br />\n嗰個都應該會行埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n渡月亭𠴱邊你都可以試下沿住桂川有路行既，我之前都見唔少本地人 hea 行，沿路河景都幾舒服。再唔係行到咁上下就去保津川坐船落返嵐山。"},{"pid":"292b8d85bfbec00fbc463666efc27b8701e9ba18","tid":108512,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:39:50.000Z","msg":"坐嵐電慢慢行都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ba1c3bfc688f7dabd9c4be82614eca0de7c2e5","tid":108512,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:46:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果去天龍寺就可以再行入 d 去埋常寂光寺𠴱頭，沿路都幾好行既。</blockquote><br />\n嗰個都應該會行埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n渡月亭𠴱邊你都可以試下沿住桂川有路行既，我之前都見唔少本地人 hea 行，沿路河景都幾舒服。再唔係行到咁上下就去保津川坐船落返嵐山。</blockquote><br />\n睇啲blog啲相好靚咁，thx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}